
query_heart_beat(3)  LPC LIBRARY FUNCTIONS    query_heart_beat(3)

NAME
     query_heart_beat() - query the status of an object's  heart-
     beat

SYNOPSIS
     int query_heart_beat();

DESCRIPTION
     Returns the  value  with  which  set_heart_beat()  has  been
     called with on this object.  If the object has no heartbeat,
     0 will be returned.

SEE ALSO
     heart_beat(4), set_heart_beat(3)


